- **Min SDK**: 29 | **Target SDK**: 35 | **Compile SDK**: 36

## Architecture (MVVM)

```
app/src/main/kotlin/{{ package_identifier | replace('.', '/') }}/
  di/            → Hilt modules
  navigation/    → NavHost + type-safe routes
  data/
    remote/      → Retrofit 3 ApiService + AuthInterceptor
    local/       → DataStore TokenStorage + Room database
    local/db/    → Room entities, DAOs, AppDatabase
    repository/  → Repository interfaces + implementations
  domain/model/  → DTOs (kotlinx.serialization)
  ui/
    theme/       → Material3 theme (from design tokens)
    auth/        → LoginScreen + LoginViewModel
    examples/    → ExampleListScreen + ExampleListViewModel
    common/      → LoadingIndicator, ErrorView
```

## MVVM Pattern

- **ViewModel**: `@HiltViewModel` with `StateFlow<UiState>`
- **UiState**: sealed interface — `Idle`, `Loading`, `Success(data)`, `Error(message)`
- **View**: `@Composable` functions, collect state with `collectAsState()`
- **DI**: Hilt (`@Inject`, `@Singleton`, `@HiltViewModel`)
- **Navigation**: Type-safe routes via `@Serializable` data objects/classes

## Conventions

- One ViewModel per screen, injected via `hiltViewModel()`
- Repositories are interfaces with `Impl` classes, Hilt-bound in `AppModule`
- API base URL configured via `buildConfigField` in `build.gradle.kts`
- Token stored in DataStore, injected into OkHttp interceptor
- Local caching via Room (entities in `data/local/db/`)
- Tests use MockK + Turbine for Flow testing

## Key Files

- `di/AppModule.kt` — all Hilt bindings (network, database, repositories)
- `data/remote/ApiService.kt` — Retrofit 3 interface matching OpenAPI
- `data/local/TokenStorage.kt` — DataStore token persistence
- `data/local/db/AppDatabase.kt` — Room database
- `ui/theme/Theme.kt` — Material3 theme from design tokens
